4.5 km. (by air and 7.1 km.( by road) E of Pucará on road to Vallegrande, degraded cloud forest, with Podocarpus parlatorei, Vallea stipularis, Dunalia brachyacantha. Occasional patches seen, mostly in still wooded or scrubby ravines from Vallegrane to Pucará, and one colony a few km. S of Pucará on road to new bridge over Río Grande at Santa Rosa. All seen were in the same stage of full flowering.

Mpio. Padcaya. Area de Influencia Reserva Nacional de Flora y Fauna Tariquía. Serrania Sidras. Campamento de guardaparques Sidras, sendero hacia la Parcela de Argentinos. Bosque Premontano, Tucumano Boliviano. Dosel 20 m, emergentes en la pendiente superior y cimas Tipuana tipu, Anadenanthera colubrina, en la pendiente inferior dominan las lauraceas.
